                    were replaced by Proper-noun capitalization).</p>
                <p>The unchanging parts of alternate names from Barsoum (<idno type="URI"
                        >http://syriaca.org/bibl/2</idno>, <idno type="URI"
                        >http://syriaca.org/bibl/3</idno>, or <idno type="URI"
                        >http://syriaca.org/bibl/4</idno>) have been supplied to each alternate.</p>
                <p>Names from the English translation of Barsoum (<idno type="URI"
                        >http://syriaca.org/bibl/4</idno>) were put in sentence word order rather
                    than fronting a dictionary headword. Any commas in the Barsoum name in English
                    were removed.</p>
                <p>The <gi>state</gi> element of @type="existence" indicates the period for which
